Methodology
Not
all
0%
APR
cards
are
created
equally.
To
generate
our
list
of
top
picks
for
0%
APR
credit
cards,
Forbes
Advisor
reviewed
dozens
of
0%
APR
credit
cards
across
a
broad
spectrum
of
issuers.
We
weighed
a
number
of
factors
including
the
length
of
a
card’s
0%
APR
offer,
any
welcome
bonuses
and
any
credit
card
fees
as
part
of
ownership
and/or
ability
to
transfer
a
balance
from
another
card.
We
also
considered
the
usefulness
of
the
card
beyond
the
intro
APR
period
including
if
it
earned
rewards
on
purchases.
The
Best
0%
APR
Credit
Cards
