to
1.8%.
That,
plus
an
introductory
offer
of
0%
Intro
APR
for
15
months
from
account
opening
on
purchases
and
balance
transfers,
then
a
variable
APR
of
14.49%
-
24.99%
fixed
APR
on
purchases
and
balance
transfers
based
on
your
creditworthiness
makes
this
card
a
tempting
choice.
